title: Abraham Lincoln Birthplace National Historical Park: News Releases
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     News     News Releases               News Releases           Subscribe  | What is RSS     August 06, 2016  Abraham Lincoln Birthplace Invites Everyone to Find Your Park during the Centennial Birthday Month  The Abraham Lincoln Birthplace National Historical Park invites everyone to #FindYourPark during the National Park Service Centennial Birthday Month!   April 01, 2016  National Park Service Launches Kentucky National Park Pentathlon  The National Park Service has launched a Kentucky National Park Pentathlon in recognition of the five national parks in Kentucky.
